# License Header Standards

## Overview

All source files must include a consistent BSD-2-Clause license header at the beginning of the file.

## License Header Format

```
// SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-2-Clause
// Copyright (c) 2026, Timo Pallach (timo@pallach.de).
```

## File Type Specific Headers

### Go Files (.go)

```go
// SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-2-Clause
// Copyright (c) 2026, Timo Pallach (timo@pallach.de).

package sylve
```

### Shell Scripts (.sh)

```bash
#!/bin/sh

# SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-2-Clause
# Copyright (c) 2026, Timo Pallach (timo@pallach.de).

# ===============================================================================
# Script Name and Purpose
# ===============================================================================
#
# Brief description of what the script does and its main purpose.
#
# The script performs the following tasks:
# 1. First major task or step
# 2. Second major task or step
# 3. Third major task or step
#
# Usage:
#   ./script_name.sh [optional arguments]
#
# Dependencies:
#   - Required tool or package
#
# Exit Codes:
#   0 - Success
#   1 - First error condition
#   2 - Second error condition
#
# ===============================================================================
```

### HCL/Packer Files (.hcl, .pkr.hcl)

```hcl
# SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-2-Clause
# Copyright (c) 2026, Timo Pallach (timo@pallach.de).
```

### TOML Files (.toml)

```toml
# SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-2-Clause
# Copyright (c) 2026, Timo Pallach (timo@pallach.de).
```

### Markdown Files (.md, .mdx)

```markdown
<!-- SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-2-Clause -->
<!-- Copyright (c) 2026, Timo Pallach (timo@pallach.de). -->

# Document Title
```

### YAML Files (.yml, .yaml)

```yaml
# SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-2-Clause
# Copyright (c) 2026, Timo Pallach (timo@pallach.de).
```

### JSON Files (.json)

JSON does not support comments; omit the license header for JSON files unless the tool consuming the file supports a `_comment` key convention.

### C/Header Files (.c, .h)

```c
// SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-2-Clause
// Copyright (c) 2026, Timo Pallach (timo@pallach.de).
```

## Examples

### Good License Header — Go File

```go
// SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-2-Clause
// Copyright (c) 2026, Timo Pallach (timo@pallach.de).

// Package sylve implements the Packer builder for Sylve-managed Bhyve VMs.
package sylve

import (
    "context"
)
```

### Good License Header — Shell Script

```bash
#!/bin/sh

# SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-2-Clause
# Copyright (c) 2026, Timo Pallach (timo@pallach.de).

# ===============================================================================
# Run Unit Tests
# ===============================================================================
#
# Runs the Go unit test suite with coverage reporting.
#
# Usage:
#   ./bin/run_unit_tests.sh
#
# Dependencies:
#   - go
#
# Exit Codes:
#   0 - All tests passed
#   1 - Tests failed
#
# ===============================================================================

set -eu

script_name="$(basename "${0}")"
```

### Good License Header — HCL Template

```hcl
# SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-2-Clause
# Copyright (c) 2026, Timo Pallach (timo@pallach.de).

packer {
  required_plugins {
    sylve = {
      version = ">= 0.1.0"
      source  = "github.com/xoro/sylve"
    }
  }
}
```
